description:
Privacy Chian(PYC) platform is an application platform for block chain asset privacy anonymity launched by the Hidden Chain Foundation.

PYC is developed by the top European virtual currency development team, which has been devoted to the development of block chain mining technology and privacy anonymity technology. In today’s era when the environment and influence of the block chain industry are expanding, the rapid development of the industry has brought about a contradiction between the crazy growth of specialization and large-scale digital mining and the universal demand of the general market. From infrastructure to electricity, from cost to technology, all of these have created certain obstacles to the market of asset privacy. PYC Foundation, as an organization with professional level and coin protocol technology, has a perfect system and experience in terms of basic resources, professional technology, energy integration and organizational management.
name: PrivacyChain
